# Gielinor Travels
This plugin adds a new distraction and diversion type mini game to Old School RuneScape, that not only tests your map knowledge, but your transportation knowledge as well.

https://gielinortravels.containers.uwcs.co.uk

*Please keep in mind that due to the images being automatically generated, some destinations may be inaccessible.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CFtJxQP3Oak
